<paragraph blockId="5.[813,1420,1909,2091]" pageId="5" pageNumber="320">This species is characterized by the white margin in dorsal, anal and caudal fins; 3–3½ scales between the lateral line and the base of the anterior dorsal-fin rays;</paragraph>
